title Tenant Onboarding Flow
direction down

Step1 [color: blue] {
  Invitation [icon: mail]
  Workspace owner sends an invitation to a user. [shape: text]
}

Step2 [color: blue] {
  Accept Invitation [icon: user-check]
  User accepts the invitation to join the workspace. [shape: text]
}

Step3 [color: green] {
  Create Account [icon: user-plus]
  User creates an account in the platform. [shape: text]
}

Step4 [color: green] {
  Sign In [icon: lock]
  User signs in to the platform. [shape: text]
}

Step5 [color: purple] {
  Access Workspace [icon: building]
  User accesses the workspace and dashboard. [shape: text]
}

Step6 [color: orange] {
  Connect Channels [icon: plug]
  User connects external communication channels. [shape: text]
}

Step7 [color: yellow] {
  Configure AI Assistant [icon: bot]
  User configures AI assistant preferences and behavior. [shape: text]
}

Step8 [color: cyan] {
  Add Knowledge Sources [icon: book-open]
  User adds documents and builds a knowledge base. [shape: text]
}

Step9 [color: blue] {
  Ready to Operate [icon: check-circle]
  Workspace is ready to receive customer messages. [shape: text]
}

Invitation > Workspace owner sends an invitation to a user.
Accept Invitation > User accepts the invitation to join the workspace.
Create Account > User creates an account in the platform.
Sign In > User signs in to the platform.
Access Workspace > User accesses the workspace and dashboard.
Connect Channels > User connects external communication channels.
Configure AI Assistant > User configures AI assistant preferences and behavior.
Add Knowledge Sources > User adds documents and builds a knowledge base.
Ready to Operate > Workspace is ready to receive customer messages.

Invitation > Accept Invitation
Accept Invitation > Create Account
Create Account > Sign In
Sign In > Access Workspace
Access Workspace > Connect Channels
Connect Channels > Configure AI Assistant
Configure AI Assistant > Add Knowledge Sources
Add Knowledge Sources > Ready to Operate